cs.RO, cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR 

Reasoning: 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is the most likely category as the paper presents a new dataset of aerial imagery captured from a robotics simulator. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is also likely as the dataset can be used for visual odometry and SLAM algorithms. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) are possible categories as the paper mentions the development and benchmarking of new algorithms for high-altitude flights. 
- cs.GR (Graphics) is also a possible category as the dataset was captured using orthophoto maps as a ground plane.
